description:
Patolicken was an Imperial Rear Admiral who served under http://anidb.net/ch190 [Karl Gustav Kempf]. He was killed when his flagship, the http://anidb.net/ch97354 [Langenberg], was destroyed during the Eighth Battle of http://anidb.net/ch1762 [Iserlohn].
Source: Gineipaedia
name: Patolicken
